== Backend
* sudoku generator for SolvedSudokus
* Also store squares in SolvedSudoku to find the adjoining sudoku faster

== App
* Sudoku: Export missing numbers as 0
* devise

== Frontend
* number selector (dial, esc-key to close)
* send number, col, row, sudoku_id to server
* extend board by another sudoku (add a rect with hover question)
* show users stats
* show user signup form (just email address and name)
* Drag the board